headline: GTA+
subtitle: Join GTA+ for Benefits
content:
Join GTA Online’s premium Membership program, delivering exclusive benefits and rewards to GTA+ Members each month, including GTA$500,000 and more. GTA+ Members can claim the below through February 4:

— Early access to the new Pfister Astrale (Sports Classic)
— 50% off Auto Shop properties and free Style Upgrades
— 2X Rewards on Auto Shop Robbery Contract Finales
— The Pfister Chore Jacket
— And more

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
